{"type": "article", "id": 50450, "title": "Dior Homme 总裁去执掌 Fendi，以及，Converse 开快闪酒店 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-22T02:14:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 2114, "name": "Bottega Veneta"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 1549, "name": "Kering"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180222095455nQdJ7i6zuoxpb50K.jpeg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-bites/lvmh-and-kering-launch-wecareformodels-com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 和开云集团联合创办 WeCareForModels.com</strong></a> | 自去年九月 LVMH 与开云集团联合发布模特工作关系与健康保障纲领之后，两大奢侈品集团再度合作，发起网站 WeCareForModels.com，旨在为模特提供精神和身体健康方面的建议及讯息。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/exclusive-serge-brunschwig-named-chairman-ceo-of-fendi-1202572784/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 集团任命 Dior Homme 总裁执掌 Fendi</strong></a> | 奢侈品集团 LVMH 任命 Dior Homme 总裁 Serge Brunschwig 为 Fendi 首席执行官，上任后， Serge Brunschwig 直接向 LVMH 董事总经理 Antonio Belloni 汇报工作。 Serge Brunschwig 曾担任 Celine 全球总裁兼 CEO，2015 年起被任命为 Dior Homme 总裁，兼任品牌首席运营官。Fendi 原首席执行官 Pietro Beccari 加入 Dior 时装部门担任首席执行官。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Italian-investor-looks-to-rev-up-Shanghai-Tang-sales,950456.html#.Wo4hj5P1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>意大利投资者看好“上海滩”销售增长 </strong></a>| 据路途社消息，意大利企业家 Alessandro Bastagli 宣布已为奢侈品牌“上海滩” 注入了一笔“重要”的资金，将帮助品牌恢复增长，预计明年实现 15-20% 的年增长。去年， Alessandro Bastagli 从历峰集团手中买下“上海滩”，品牌年销售额约 4000 万欧元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/565152\" rel=\"nofollow\">优衣库将与 Tomas Maier 合作推出假日系列。</a>Tomas 自 2001 年起担任 Bottega Veneta 的创意总监，并有自己的同名品牌 Tomas Maier。 </p><p>该系列将于今年初夏正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095759iNgfehHMPmpTkn19.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562225\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>伦敦时装周上，<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/burberry-ss18-time/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christopher Bailey 发布了他在 Burberry 的最后一个系列，名为“Time”。 </a></p><p>Bailey 称，这一季是为了庆祝 Burberry 的“过去、现在和未来”，新系列里加入了近些年大热的“购物袋”，之前透露过的彩虹元素也在该系列中多次出现。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095847YT6NUcGiuFwtpWxB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095848nAuUceLmaFsqQ6r8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095848ybEF8AQeKDfs1YaS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095847gtrq1CLnwZ7eaEIx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095848nOgLz9XDuF28eGs6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095848Ii2SDB9kXjgqo4Pl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220958488wycXnGYWuVlE124.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095847hqQERGa2X8pK5ufJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959232gExXYfkqjR6wTZt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095923ln9LXOhkWr75QaCA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095923uWa9sZGmiU1fP5XF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959247vprwSVD3uT2MGqH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095924zuj8aWlACSnB4tef.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095924cEa9xksQH6XwgTCS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095924ldKM70tO1XErPih5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095924cRNPtopjnBVZKI2X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959249cBSR7QkfKagELuG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095937EARLNdX8HT2ibZjf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095937dfGX0795Zt18VkIO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959379nHQdPfOIC2xgwXR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959371MQtNFq76e4GfjO8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095937ikQmFMGZn3Yr0jDI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095937LoYIl932vEkGbsuN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959379zZGb2MfS1FJoBD3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095937EY3cOSB7vTik29op.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095938VLrqnbkaA4c1zdvG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>为了给新系列造势，Converse 前几日在伦敦开设了首家快闪酒店，<a href=\"http://www.complex.com/sneakers/2018/02/look-inside-one-star-hotel\" rel=\"nofollow\">One Star Hotel。 </a></p><p>这家酒店仅仅开了两天，共有五层楼，还邀请了 A$AP Nast、Yung Lean、 MadeMe 等人特别策划了融合数字艺术的特别展。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000A1MbwWYKLlnJxsIU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802221000006v9bjawfN8IOZFD0.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000CvLS24xaf1OhtQRj.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222095959lftDQsik7POFNKXL.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.648182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000hUKOfYPglkHoeGd1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.648182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802220959596Yk5wbrM4mHRPDCV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000pLmx4Od0lHZXIjEU.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.667273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000WySgpJoUl1jNdVOa.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100000bH7x0nkJYOZVqWBD.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.657334\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>讨好年轻消费者，资生堂宣布开展新的产品 <a href=\"https://www.shiseidogroup.jp/news/detail.html?n=00000000002387\" rel=\"nofollow\">COSMETIC PRESS</a>，该计划以当季流行趋势和消费者喜好为主导，开发对应不同需求的期间限定品牌。目前发布的第一个彩妆品牌是 Ice Cream Parlour，共包括 4 个品类的 19 种单品，将于 3 月 20 日正式发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022210001990zLJ2yDiIrnsUeG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100019rmkS4wpD39RcQlAE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100019nxBrJpbci6AKsRuj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周上，Moncler 发布了名为<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/milan/moncler-genius/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“想象力共和国”</a>的新系列。 </p><p>该系列是 Moncler Genius 计划的第一弹，这个计划邀请了 Valentino 创意总监 Pierpaolo Piccioli、知名造型师 Karl Templer、川久保玲的徒弟 Kei Ninomiya、设计师 Simone Rocha 及 Sandro Mandrino，潮流教父藤原浩、英国设计师 Craig Green 以及 Moncler 的艺术总监 Francesco Ragazzi 共同创作。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100034oTEnl9PQ0eKZcgsF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100034ezjTKEMkytSn4fGv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100034W4VR9jJhcKlBu8d2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802221000351vx9nMZG4JfHDAEY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100035w9RJ0uyO8W1I4cCD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100035eq8V9Kvn2arY0xgZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100035OmvhWx04fXEdut2Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100035IDhGeF01EVkYijnu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802221000364l9SaBEVngAf0XvY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100056SDQxF6bYemJWsjGy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100056NOVaQicnur4hqmL3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100055HIZYkchCy19AdOnj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.521739\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100056IBpWHZ5PzbEReOL0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100056p3oQjZAWY67KN5dc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802221000567Jr5Lw4nluBVmROW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100056qgRNQaFzPZKlHEmv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100057aI6zwWiCcpRvJF1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100057Tjg5Md6fzNsDmI2u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100057f5cBtpFRk8o7jMDr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180222100057aDiMI9rudkoB1Gyj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802221001150fY5Z8wE3UaTqbmK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure>